***************************
* The Switchable Painting *
***************************

Dissertation project at Imperial College London.

Description
===========

The purpose of the project is to enhance art discovery through augmented reality. It takes the form
of an Android application which can extract and recognize paintings from walls and overlay recommended
paintings over them, hence 'switching' them out.

Components
==========

android/: Android application.
ors/: A Java HTTP service using my RSJWS framework, performing online image recognition using SIFT.
server/: A Python Tornado proxy server for image uploads and more.
recs/: A painting recommendation service.